{{Youmay|the Nebulon-B Frigate ''Virulence''|[[Errant Venture/Legends|the ''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer ''Virulence'']], later renamed ''Errant Venture''}}
'''''Virulence''''' was an [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The ''Virulence'' responded to a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] attack on an unguarded [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] repair dock as part of the Alliance's testing of the [[R-22 Spearhead starfighter|R-22 Spearhead]] but arrived too late to prevent the destruction of the facility.

